query:
WITH workout_id AS (
            SELECT id
            FROM workout
            WHERE workout_uid = $1
        )
        SELECT
            variant AS "variant!: ExerciseVariant",
            description AS "description!",
            weight AS "weight!",
            reps AS "reps!",
            sets AS "sets!",
            rpe
        FROM structured_exercise se
        WHERE se.workout_id = workout_id

        UNION ALL

        SELECT
            variant AS "variant!: ExerciseVariant",
            description AS "description!",
            weight AS "weight!",
            reps AS "reps!",
            sets AS "sets!",
            rpe
        FROM freeform_exercise fe
        WHERE fe.workout_id = workout_id
